welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Eching, Germany! Get ready to experience the warmth and charm of our beautiful city, known for its stunning landscapes and rich history. We invite you to explore and indulge in all that Eching has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Franz Josef Strauss Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: The secondary terminal at Franz Josef Strauss Airport, primarily serving budget airlines and some international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. Premium options are also available for purchase.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Fuerstenfeldbruck Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Fuerstenfeldbruck Airport, mainly used for regional and low-cost carriers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. No login or password is required.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Oberpfaffenhofen Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: A separate terminal for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
